# Challenge :
# Using the Ruby language, have the function TimeConvert(num) take 
# the num parameter being passed and
# return the number of hours and minutes the parameter converts 
# to (ie. if num = 63 then the output should be 1:3). 
# Separate the number of hours and minutes with a colon.

# Solution: 
def TimeConvert(num)
  hours = num / 60
  minutes = num - (hours * 60)
  reminder = num % 60 if num % 60 != 0
  case
  when reminder == true
    puts "#{0}:#{reminder}"
  else
    puts "#{hours}:#{minutes}"
  end
end                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       

TimeConvert(126) == '2:6'
TimeConvert(45) == '0:45'